  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\nCurrently, after some errors (could check only on \"Wrong card\" error, not sure how to trigger another) during signing transaction, you can't continue signing until canceling current state (closing bottom sheet for signing) and after redirecting to signing phrase bottom sheet custom keyboard for entering PIN code is hidden.\r\n \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n5) \"Wrong card\" is shown\r\n6) Signing the bottom sheet is not changed\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n5) Can sign transaction\r\n6) The custom keyboard for entering PIN-code is hidden if error appears on signing (i.e. wrong card error)\r\n![photo_2020-04-27 10 41 21](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/80352087-a6d7d280-8873-11ea-8cbb-2db53a2a6604.jpeg)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n1) Create account with keycard\r\n2) Open wallet -> send transaction -> enter valid amount and recipient -> Next -> proceed to Sign with keycard\r\n3) Enter PIN code and trigger error (the  simplest way is to use Wrong card)\r\n![photo_2020-04-27 10 44 29](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/80352382-1948b280-8874-11ea-83a6-92f9f4684e25.jpeg)\r\n4) Tap on OK\r\n5) Use right card (here expected that transaction will be signed, instead of that one more \"Wrong card\" error is triggered)\r\n6) Tap on Cancel\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n- Status version: nightly 24/04/2020\r\n- Operating System: Android\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n[Status-debug-logs-1.zip](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/4538446/Status-debug-logs-1.zip)\r\n\r\n",
